---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const lastUpdated = "May 14, 2026";
---
<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Golf Cart Rentals The Villages"
  description="Privacy policy for Golf Cart Rentals The Villages - how we collect, use, and protect information from customers and website visitors."
  noindex={false}
>
  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-brand-600 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading font-black text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-4">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <article class="prose prose-slate max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Golf Cart Rentals The Villages (&ldquo;we,&rdquo; &ldquo;us,&rdquo; or &ldquo;our&rdquo;) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect personal information when you visit our website or rent a golf cart from us.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Contact details</strong> you submit through our quote and contact forms - name, phone number, email address, and delivery address.</li>
        <li><strong>Booking details</strong> needed to fulfill your rental, including rental dates, cart preference, and payment information processed by our secure payment provider.</li>
        <li><strong>Site usage data</strong> like browser type, pages visited, and approximate location, collected through cookies and standard analytics.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>To respond to quote requests and schedule deliveries.</li>
        <li>To process payments and manage active rentals.</li>
        <li>To send booking confirmations, reminders, and follow-up messages by phone, text, or email - only related to your rental.</li>
        <li>To improve the website and our services.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">SMS &amp; Text Messaging</h2>
      <p>
        If you check the SMS consent box on any form, you agree to receive text messages from us related to your rental (booking confirmations, delivery times, follow-ups). Message and data rates may apply. Reply <strong>STOP</strong> to opt out at any time, or <strong>HELP</strong> for help. We do not share or sell your phone number to third parties for marketing.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell your personal information. We share data only with service providers that help us operate (payment processing, hosting, analytics, scheduling, SMS delivery) and only as needed to provide our services. We may disclose information if required by law.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        We use industry-standard security practices to protect your personal information, including encrypted form submissions, secure payment processing through trusted providers, and access controls on customer records. No system is 100% secure, but we work hard to keep your data safe.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p>
        We use cookies and similar technologies to remember preferences, keep the site working, and measure traffic through standard analytics. You can disable cookies in your browser, but some site features may stop working. We do not use cookies for cross-site advertising or to build behavioral profiles of visitors.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>
        Our site may link to third-party websites (Google Maps, social media, payment processors). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites - please review their privacy policies before sharing personal information with them.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You can request a copy of the personal information we hold about you, ask us to correct or delete it, or opt out of marketing messages at any time. Email <a href="mailto:villages@mastersgolfcars.com" class="text-brand-600 font-bold">villages@mastersgolfcars.com</a> with your request.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">Children</h2>
      <p>
        Our services are intended for adults. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date above shows when the policy was last revised. Material changes will be highlighted on this page.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions? Reach us at <a href="mailto:villages@mastersgolfcars.com" class="text-brand-600 font-bold">villages@mastersgolfcars.com</a> or <a href="tel:+13523064409" class="text-brand-600 font-bold">(352) 306-4409</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
